1
00:00:05,950 --> 00:00:07,910
[Lee Dong Won as Seung Jun]

2
00:00:07,910 --> 00:00:09,630
[Seong Tae as Jae Hyeon]

3
00:00:09,630 --> 00:00:11,310
[Shin Myeong Seong as Ho Yeon]

4
00:00:11,310 --> 00:00:13,080
[Kim Gyu Jong as Ju Won]

5
00:00:35,573 --> 00:00:44,473
[Happy Merry Ending]

6
00:00:48,190 --> 00:00:55,590
♫ Quietly my two lips come together ♫

7
00:00:55,590 --> 00:01:01,390
♫ And call out your name ♫

8
00:01:02,990 --> 00:01:10,260
♫ Before I knew it, my empty days became filled ♫

9
00:01:10,260 --> 00:01:16,820
♫ With you and memories of you ♫

10
00:01:16,820 --> 00:01:18,804
♫ When I close my eyes ♫

11
00:01:18,804 --> 00:01:22,334
That was how we met again.

12
00:01:22,334 --> 00:01:29,250
[Episode 1: The Man Who Entered My Heart]

13
00:01:45,834 --> 00:01:47,800
Ugh, seriously?

14
00:01:50,302 --> 00:01:51,776
Did you sleep well?

15
00:01:51,776 --> 00:01:54,751
Sleep in your own house, will you?

16
00:01:54,751 --> 00:01:56,890
You don't sleep well on your own.

17
00:01:56,890 --> 00:02:00,330
I moved in upstairs so that I could be near you.

18
00:02:13,600 --> 00:02:15,583
I'm late…

19
00:02:16,510 --> 00:02:18,840
[Villa de GD]
[GD Convention | GD Party House | GD Wedding Mall]

20
00:02:18,840 --> 00:02:22,193
- Was it difficult to get here?
- Oh my god! Congratulations. You look gorgeous.

21
00:02:22,193 --> 00:02:24,460
- So pretty.
- Thank you! Let's take a picture.

22
00:02:24,460 --> 00:02:27,210
Okay. One, two, three.

23
00:02:29,083 --> 00:02:31,351
Have you heard from him?

24
00:02:32,167 --> 00:02:34,734
N-Not yet.

25
00:02:36,559 --> 00:02:38,725
But it should be fine, right?

26
00:02:39,618 --> 00:02:42,334
Of course not!

27
00:02:42,334 --> 00:02:44,542
What on earth is going on?

28
00:02:44,542 --> 00:02:48,125
Did you really not hear a single one of my alarms going off?

29
00:02:48,125 --> 00:02:51,083
You are late anyway, so come back to bed. Let's sleep some more, okay?

30
00:02:51,083 --> 00:02:52,714
You turned off the alarm, didn't you?

31
00:02:52,714 --> 00:02:54,400
No.

32
00:02:54,400 --> 00:02:56,110
Where are the black socks?

33
00:02:56,110 --> 00:02:58,076
In the laundry basket.

34
00:03:00,138 --> 00:03:05,018
I told you not to wear mine. Or at least wash them.

35
00:03:05,018 --> 00:03:08,250
- Where's my jacket?
- Look carefully. It must be somewhere.

36
00:03:08,250 --> 00:03:10,934
Oh! It might be at my place…

37
00:03:10,934 --> 00:03:14,059
Why is nothing where it's supposed to be? Damn it.

38
00:03:20,429 --> 00:03:23,010
- Hey, Seung Jun!
- What?

39
00:03:24,872 --> 00:03:26,542
You're lost without that, right?

40
00:03:26,542 --> 00:03:28,334
You are a lifesaver. Thanks.

41
00:03:28,334 --> 00:03:31,150
- Do you have everything?
- See you later.

42
00:04:24,083 --> 00:04:26,199
Oh, I'm so nervous!

43
00:04:26,199 --> 00:04:28,992
- Don't be! You are the prettiest one here!
- Really?

44
00:04:28,992 --> 00:04:30,841
- I have to go. See you later.
- See you.

45
00:04:30,841 --> 00:04:32,506
Ladies and Gentlemen, may I have your attention, please?

46
00:04:32,506 --> 00:04:37,018
The wedding ceremony will begin soon, so please come into the ceremony hall and take your seats.

47
00:04:37,018 --> 00:04:39,183
Are you kidding me…

48
00:04:39,183 --> 00:04:41,517
Team Leader,

49
00:04:41,517 --> 00:04:43,684
he's not answering his phone.

50
00:04:43,684 --> 00:04:46,209
What if he ran away?

51
00:04:46,209 --> 00:04:47,992
No way.

52
00:04:47,992 --> 00:04:50,242
Why is this happening?

53
00:04:50,242 --> 00:04:52,025
Excuse me.

54
00:04:52,700 --> 00:04:53,909
Yes?

55
00:04:53,909 --> 00:04:56,283
How much time do we have left?

56
00:04:56,283 --> 00:05:01,359
Oh, the time! About five minutes.

57
00:05:23,882 --> 00:05:26,115
He should be fine, right?

58
00:06:01,545 --> 00:06:04,079
I can do it!

59
00:06:04,079 --> 00:06:05,642
I got this!

60
00:06:05,642 --> 00:06:08,875
Let's hope that the bride and groom will have a bright future together. And with your best wishes,

61
00:06:08,875 --> 00:06:12,263
please give them one more big round of applause!

62
00:06:23,367 --> 00:06:25,834
Who's that? Is he blind?

63
00:06:26,717 --> 00:06:29,584
What's with the sunglasses?

64
00:06:31,933 --> 00:06:40,058
Now we will hear the long-awaited song in celebration of the bride and groom's everlasting union!

65
00:07:05,508 --> 00:07:09,800
♪ Though the heart cannot be heard ♪

66
00:07:12,659 --> 00:07:16,300
♪ Or seen ♪

67
00:07:19,823 --> 00:07:30,899
♪ Somehow we're standing here facing each other ♪

68
00:07:33,842 --> 00:07:38,459
♪ What is love? ♪

69
00:07:40,867 --> 00:07:45,450
♪ Does it last forever? ♪

70
00:07:46,550 --> 00:07:53,759
♪ I still can't give you an answer ♪

71
00:07:53,759 --> 00:08:00,342
♪ But I will tell you my true feelings ♪

72
00:08:00,342 --> 00:08:06,542
♪ Can I stand by your side now? ♪

73
00:08:07,187 --> 00:08:14,051
♪ Maybe we are destined to be together ♪

74
00:08:14,051 --> 00:08:20,750
♪ A dream we've been hiding for so long ♪

75
00:08:21,926 --> 00:08:29,367
♪ You are mine, and I am yours, us together ♪

76
00:08:36,058 --> 00:08:38,517
You still play well.

77
00:08:38,517 --> 00:08:41,171
Of course, I do. I have been playing the piano for years.

78
00:08:41,171 --> 00:08:43,520
You should work here part-time.

79
00:08:43,520 --> 00:08:45,860
It's so hard to find an accompanist.

80
00:08:45,867 --> 00:08:49,362
I can't leave the shop on weekends. That's when we have the most customers.

81
00:08:49,362 --> 00:08:51,589
But I'll drop by to see you from time to time.

82
00:08:51,589 --> 00:08:54,267
Anyway, who was that earlier?

83
00:08:54,267 --> 00:08:55,385
Who?

84
00:08:55,385 --> 00:08:57,145
The one with the sunglasses.

85
00:08:57,145 --> 00:08:59,080
He was hilarious.

86
00:08:59,080 --> 00:09:01,667
Seung Jun? He's the singer here.

87
00:09:01,667 --> 00:09:05,376
I've known him for a long time, but he's still a mystery.

88
00:09:06,170 --> 00:09:08,170
Here he comes.

89
00:09:16,187 --> 00:09:18,978
This is Lee Seung Jun, the pride of our wedding hall.

90
00:09:18,978 --> 00:09:21,861
And this is Song Jae Hyeon, our substitute for today.

91
00:09:34,162 --> 00:09:35,928
Jae Hyeon!

92
00:09:35,928 --> 00:09:37,987
Ah… Yes…

93
00:09:37,987 --> 00:09:42,178
Hi, I'm Song Jae Hyeon, and I will be working with you from now on.

94
00:09:43,245 --> 00:09:44,854
I look forward to working with you.

95
00:09:44,854 --> 00:09:47,721
Ah, yes.

96
00:09:49,564 --> 00:09:52,567
You are an amazing singer.

97
00:09:52,567 --> 00:09:56,603
And you're really good-looking without the sunglasses.

98
00:09:56,603 --> 00:10:00,286
He's a little shy.

99
00:10:00,862 --> 00:10:02,863
So you're taking the job, right?

100
00:10:02,863 --> 00:10:05,746
I told you, I have always wanted to do this.

101
00:10:06,336 --> 00:10:10,045
We are a family now, so why don't we go out for a company meal together?

102
00:10:10,045 --> 00:10:13,269
- Is that all right?
- Sounds good to me.

103
00:10:13,269 --> 00:10:16,046
Sorry, I have to go now.

104
00:10:16,046 --> 00:10:18,004
Ah... okay.

105
00:10:21,354 --> 00:10:26,328
What? How could he just leave like that in the middle of a conversation?

106
00:10:26,328 --> 00:10:30,062
You should give up now. Seung Jun is a tough nut to crack.

107
00:10:30,062 --> 00:10:33,461
Even we have never had a meal with him.

108
00:10:35,936 --> 00:10:39,403
I will bring him with me! Can you make the reservation?

109
00:10:40,370 --> 00:10:42,020
What?

110
00:10:46,187 --> 00:10:47,770
Seung Jun!

111
00:10:47,770 --> 00:10:49,525
Come join us. Please?

112
00:10:49,525 --> 00:10:53,101
Do you have an important appointment or something? It's not like that, is it?

113
00:10:53,962 --> 00:10:55,803
I'm sorry.

114
00:11:02,162 --> 00:11:04,245
Are you okay?

115
00:11:04,245 --> 00:11:05,764
Yes.

116
00:11:06,950 --> 00:11:10,412
Seung Jun, you've never been to a company dinner before, have you?

117
00:11:10,412 --> 00:11:13,628
It's basic manners to at least show up.

118
00:11:14,661 --> 00:11:17,054
Just sit with us for half an hour.

119
00:11:17,860 --> 00:11:19,363
Or just ten minutes?

120
00:11:19,363 --> 00:11:21,096
Five minutes?

121
00:11:24,312 --> 00:11:27,370
Great work today, everyone!

122
00:11:27,370 --> 00:11:31,536
Now, now! We have a new member with us, and it's Seung Jun's first time joining us.

123
00:11:31,536 --> 00:11:35,162
So a toast is in order. Let's go with the usual.

124
00:11:35,162 --> 00:11:39,236
- Here's to our...
- Romantic weekends!

125
00:11:43,870 --> 00:11:47,586
The vibe at our get-togethers has never been this good.

126
00:11:47,586 --> 00:11:51,470
This is all thanks to you, Seung Jun. You should join us more often.

127
00:11:51,470 --> 00:11:56,078
Yes, we've worked together for more than two years, and we've never even had a meal together.

128
00:11:56,078 --> 00:11:58,051
I never mentioned it, but it hurt my feelings.

129
00:11:58,051 --> 00:12:00,087
I practically had to drag him here.

130
00:12:00,087 --> 00:12:04,058
Really? I wish I could have seen it!

131
00:12:04,058 --> 00:12:06,961
Let's get together more often!

132
00:12:06,961 --> 00:12:09,090
That sounds great!

133
00:12:09,090 --> 00:12:12,160
I know, right?

134
00:12:12,832 --> 00:12:14,995
Seung Jun,

135
00:12:14,995 --> 00:12:19,112
can I ask you something?

136
00:12:19,911 --> 00:12:22,150
Why do you wear those sunglasses?

137
00:12:22,150 --> 00:12:24,570
You are so handsome.

138
00:12:25,203 --> 00:12:29,511
I'm not quite comfortable with people staring,

139
00:12:31,536 --> 00:12:33,886
so when there's a crowd...

140
00:12:41,719 --> 00:12:43,412
He was just taking care of you because he felt sorry for you…

141
00:12:43,412 --> 00:12:45,678
- Get yourself together, for God's sake…
- Don't you think it's too late…

142
00:12:45,678 --> 00:12:47,762
- Do better!
- Aren't you ashamed to see the other members?

143
00:12:47,762 --> 00:12:50,511
- Well, too bad! Looks like he abandoned you…
- Don't flatter yourself!

144
00:12:50,511 --> 00:12:52,155
Seung Jun, Seung Jun…

145
00:12:52,155 --> 00:12:53,572
Seung Jun!

146
00:12:53,572 --> 00:12:55,131
Are you all right, Seung Jun?

147
00:12:55,131 --> 00:12:57,089
Ah… I am sorry.

148
00:12:57,089 --> 00:13:00,383
I… I have to go to the bathroom.

149
00:13:04,047 --> 00:13:06,614
Did I… do something wrong?

150
00:13:06,614 --> 00:13:08,156
No…

151
00:13:08,156 --> 00:13:12,490
He was always a bit strange, but we didn't know how serious it was.

152
00:13:12,490 --> 00:13:17,660
Don't worry about it. We were all curious, right?

153
00:13:17,660 --> 00:13:19,240
Right.

154
00:13:27,755 --> 00:13:29,914
[Antidepressants]

155
00:13:47,386 --> 00:13:49,100
Seung Jun!

156
00:14:11,547 --> 00:14:13,437
You're seeing someone, aren't you?

157
00:14:13,437 --> 00:14:15,188
[Song Jae Hyeon: Seung Jun, are you busy?]

158
00:14:15,188 --> 00:14:16,320
[Vocal Trainer | Lee Seung Jun]

159
00:14:18,633 --> 00:14:21,222
Why are you here…

160
00:14:21,222 --> 00:14:23,838
I'm... not going anywhere.

161
00:14:23,838 --> 00:14:25,215
Hyeong!

162
00:14:25,215 --> 00:14:27,339
Why are you so surprised?

163
00:14:27,339 --> 00:14:31,964
I became defensive in both social and romantic relationships.
